      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect and shows its age, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option that could make a great daily beater, first car, or little project. If you want something inexpensive that gets you on the road without a huge upfront cost, this one is worth a look. Priced to sell and ready for someone practical to give it a good home.",
