      "description": "A car with honest character and a story in every mile, this is the kind of ride that speaks to drivers who appreciate grit, charm, and possibility. It has the unmistakable presence of a vehicle that\u2019s been out in the world and still has more to give\u2014ideal for someone looking for an inexpensive daily, a hands-on project, or a practical set of wheels with personality. If you like machines with soul and the chance to make something your own, this one is easy to imagine in your driveway.",
