      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with a lot of life still to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a great little project to tinker with. It has the usual signs of age and wear you\u2019d expect, but it\u2019s priced fairly and being offered by someone who believes in being straightforward. If you want something cheap, usable, and full of potential, this could be a great fit.",
